      "id": "PopularPost267500",
      "post_content": "Actually, rather than Honor of the Pure I'd say this is more the case of paying more for [Blessing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blessing). Not strictly better since you can get this out a turn earlier and this provides a bonus without spending any mana, but a +1/+1 pump is obviously much better than a +0/+1 pump for the same mana cost.  \n  \nStill, back in the day I do remember loving this for Ice Age. ",
